Date: Fri, 21 Feb 2020 05:28:24 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 050/148] FROMGIT: arm64: dts: meson: add thermal zones to
 meson gx devices

Adapt current VIM2 thermal zones support so zones are available on all
meson gx devices. This allows a cooling fan to be driven using the i2c
interface on the Khadas VIM1 and VIM2 boards.

Suggested-by: Nick Xie <nick@khadas.com>
Signed-off-by: Christian Hewitt <christianshewitt@gmail.com>
---
